export const empty = `
<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?>
<bpmn:definitions xmlns:xsi="http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema-instance" xmlns:bpmn="http://www.omg.org/spec/BPMN/20100524/MODEL" xmlns:bpmndi="http://www.omg.org/spec/BPMN/20100524/DI" xmlns:dc="http://www.omg.org/spec/DD/20100524/DC" xmlns:di="http://www.omg.org/spec/DD/20100524/DI" id="Definitions_04vqa02" targetNamespace="http://bpmn.io/schema/bpmn">
  <bpmn:process id="Process_1" isExecutable="false">
    <bpmn:startEvent id="StartEvent_1">
      <bpmn:outgoing>SequenceFlow_14aasmc</bpmn:outgoing>
    </bpmn:startEvent>
    <bpmn:sequenceFlow id="SequenceFlow_14aasmc" sourceRef="StartEvent_1" targetRef="Task_0hyro7l" />
    <bpmn:intermediateThrowEvent id="IntermediateThrowEvent_0fabdoa">
      <bpmn:incoming>SequenceFlow_0o8isry</bpmn:incoming>
    </bpmn:intermediateThrowEvent>
    <bpmn:sequenceFlow id="SequenceFlow_0o8isry" sourceRef="Task_0hyro7l" targetRef="IntermediateThrowEvent_0fabdoa" />
    <bpmn:scriptTask id="Task_0hyro7l" name="Resolve DID">
    <script>
    <![CDATA[
      const request = services.request;
      const self = this;
      request.get(self.variables.url, (err, resp, body) => {
        if (err) return next(err);
        self.variables.scriptTaskCompleted = true;
        next(null, {result: body});
      })
    ]]>
  </script>
      <bpmn:incoming>SequenceFlow_14aasmc</bpmn:incoming>
      <bpmn:outgoing>SequenceFlow_0o8isry</bpmn:outgoing>
    </bpmn:scriptTask>
  </bpmn:process>
  <bpmndi:BPMNDiagram id="BPMNDiagram_1">
    <bpmndi:BPMNPlane id="BPMNPlane_1" bpmnElement="Process_1">
      <bpmndi:BPMNShape id="_BPMNShape_StartEvent_2" bpmnElement="StartEvent_1">
        <dc:Bounds x="173" y="102" width="36" height="36" />
      </bpmndi:BPMNShape>
      <bpmndi:BPMNEdge id="SequenceFlow_14aasmc_di" bpmnElement="SequenceFlow_14aasmc">
        <di:waypoint x="209" y="120" />
        <di:waypoint x="270" y="120" />
      </bpmndi:BPMNEdge>
      <bpmndi:BPMNShape id="IntermediateThrowEvent_0fabdoa_di" bpmnElement="IntermediateThrowEvent_0fabdoa">
        <dc:Bounds x="441" y="102" width="36" height="36" />
      </bpmndi:BPMNShape>
      <bpmndi:BPMNEdge id="SequenceFlow_0o8isry_di" bpmnElement="SequenceFlow_0o8isry">
        <di:waypoint x="370" y="120" />
        <di:waypoint x="441" y="120" />
      </bpmndi:BPMNEdge>
      <bpmndi:BPMNShape id="ScriptTask_15ys8pn_di" bpmnElement="Task_0hyro7l">
        <dc:Bounds x="270" y="80" width="100" height="80" />
      </bpmndi:BPMNShape>
    </bpmndi:BPMNPlane>
  </bpmndi:BPMNDiagram>

`;
